            "size": 1145,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01FVa9ZLKUV4d6fHeSkqEJ5z\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\\n\\n---\\n\\nNow, let's spell out some unique features of your business.\\n\\nThis helps your ad take up more real estate, and gives your users more reasons to click. I filled in a few ideas to help get us started.\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"callouts\\\": [\\n    \\\"Works Across Time Zones\\\",\\n    \\\"80% Less Coordination Time\\\",\\n    \\\"2,000+ Teams Trust Us\\\",\\n    \\\"14-Day Free Trial\\\",\\n    \\\"No Credit Card Required\\\",\\n    \\\"Instant Time Suggestions\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"structuredSnippets\\\": {\\n    \\\"category\\\": \\\"Services\\\",\\n    \\\"details\\\": [\\n      \\\"Calendar Integration\\\",\\n      \\\"Availability Preferences\\\",\\n      \\\"Automated Scheduling\\\"\\n    ]\\n  }\\n}\\n```\\n\\nWhat do you think? Any of these features resonate, or should we adjust the angle?\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1700,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":199,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
