            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1451,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01DBwTXt5sEDN6Ff9jknv3aC\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I appreciate you wanting to move forward, but let's nail down your core idea first—this is the foundation for everything else!\\n\\nHere's what I need to understand: **What does your business do, and what makes it different?**\\n\\nThink about it this way:\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"type\\\": \\\"reply\\\",\\n  \\\"text\\\": \\\"I know brainstorming can feel tedious, but your core idea is the foundation for everything we build. Let me help you find a compelling angle.\\\",\\n  \\\"examples\\\": [\\n    \\\"We help busy professionals meal prep in 30 minutes using AI-generated recipes tailored to their dietary restrictions—no subscription required.\\\",\\n    \\\"We're a B2B SaaS platform that automates customer support tickets using industry-specific AI, cutting response time from hours to seconds.\\\",\\n    \\\"We sell premium, sustainable dog toys made from recycled ocean plastic—each purchase funds ocean cleanup initiatives.\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"conclusion\\\": \\\"What's your business idea? Even if it feels rough, let's shape it together into something compelling.\\\"\\n}\\n```\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":2299,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":237,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
