        "response": {
          "bodySize": 1489,
          "content": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1489,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_012bc7wjw3cavpZ4MJerKmbP\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I appreciate the enthusiasm, but I need to actually understand your business idea first! I can't build great marketing copy without knowing what you're selling and why it matters.\\n\\nLet me ask you directly: **What's your business idea? What does it do, and what makes it different from what already exists?**\\n\\nHere are some examples of what I'm looking for:\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"type\\\": \\\"reply\\\",\\n  \\\"text\\\": \\\"I need to understand your core business idea before we can move forward. What problem are you solving, and what makes your approach unique?\\\",\\n  \\\"examples\\\": [\\n    \\\"A meal prep service that delivers customized, macro-balanced meals for fitness enthusiasts who don't have time to cook\\\",\\n    \\\"An AI-powered scheduling tool for freelancers that automatically finds their most productive hours and blocks time accordingly\\\",\\n    \\\"A luxury pet grooming service that comes to your home, so your dog never has to leave the house\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"conclusion\\\": \\\"Give me 2-3 sentences about what your business does and what sets it apart. What's the core idea?\\\"\\n}\\n```\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":2309,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":248,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
