        "response": {
          "bodySize": 1328,
          "content": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1328,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001\",\"id\":\"msg_01PjgKfdwFb55bvnNvRhnLr6\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I appreciate the detail on your vetting process—that's definitely a differentiator. But I need to redirect slightly: **who is your primary customer?** Are you selling to podcast hosts, or to guests looking for podcast appearances?\\n\\nOnce I know that, I can understand their pain points better and we'll nail the audience section.\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"type\\\": \\\"reply\\\",\\n  \\\"text\\\": \\\"Let me clarify: are you primarily going after podcast hosts who need guests, or are you targeting guests/experts who want podcast appearances? Who's paying for Friend of the Pod?\\\",\\n  \\\"examples\\\": [\\n    \\\"Hosts: 'I spend 5+ hours a week finding quality guests and vetting them. I need a faster way.'\\\",\\n    \\\"Guests: 'I want podcast appearances to build my brand, but I don't know which shows to pitch or how to get booked.'\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"conclusion\\\": \\\"This will help me understand who we're writing marketing copy for.\\\"\\n}\\n```\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":2671,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":226,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
